<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.3">
<l>kūvāy pūṅkuyilē</l>
<l>kuḷirmāri taṭuttukanta</l>
<l>māvāy kīṇṭama ṇivaṇṇa ṉaivarak</l>
<l>kūvāy pūṅkuyilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Coo, pretty cuckoo;</l>
<l>The jewel-hued lord who split the horse’s mouth</l>
<l>And rejoiced blocking the cold torrent,</l>
<l>Coo [for him] to come, pretty cuckoo!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
